OL,7,Fdoctor after suffering seizures says
OL,8,Fhe "saved his life".
OL,10,FNow, there are calls for the charity
OL,11,Fsupporting volunteer medics to get
OL,12,Fmore recognition.
OL,14,FMEDSERVE is staffed by doctors and
OL,15,Fparamedics who volunteer outside their
OL,16,Fnormal work.
OL,18,FChris Webb takes medication to control
OL,19,Fhis but he still has seizures.
