OL,6,FIn the early hours of one morning in
OL,7,FJanuary this year, he started fitting
OL,8,Funcontrollably at home. His partner
OL,9,FRondine phoned for help.
OL,11,FA paramedic arrived but he couldn't
OL,12,Fstop the seizures.
OL,14,FRondine said: "He got a call to say
OL,15,Fthat a critical care doctor was coming
OL,16,Fto the property.
