OL,3,C'This might be the difference between
OL,4,Clife and death' says volunteer doctor
OL,6,F"Dr Monsell walked in and went
OL,7,Fstraight into the bathroom, and agreed
OL,8,Fwith the paramedic to try something
OL,9,Fdifferent and then he administered
OL,10,Fsome ketamine to try and stop the
OL,11,Fseizures, so that we could get him to
OL,12,FA&E."
OL,14,FLater, Chris was taken to the hospital
OL,15,Fwhere he made a full recovery. Now
OL,16,Fhe's filled with gratitude for the
OL,17,Fcare he received.
