OL,6,FMr Webb said: "100 percent (Dr Monsell
OL,7,Fsave my life). I'm thankful for that
OL,8,Fman and that organisation to be doing
OL,9,Fthat on their own behalf was
OL,10,Fabsolutely amazing. I've never met
OL,11,Fanybody like them."
OL,13,FChris was helped by a doctor from
OL,14,FMEDSERVE Wales. They are a team of
OL,15,Fvolunteer medics who give up their
OL,16,Fspare time to lend their expertise at
OL,17,Fthe scene of emergencies.
