OL,6,FWhen asked how satisfying do they find
OL,7,Fthe work, enhanced care doctor Alex
OL,8,FWilson Evans said: "That ability to be
OL,9,Fwith people at their time of need and
OL,10,Fto bring the skill set that might be
OL,11,Fthe difference between life and death
OL,12,For serious injury really does make a
OL,13,Fdifference."
OL,15,FIan Bowler, chair of MEDSERVE Wales
OL,16,Fsaid: "We can offer more enhanced
OL,17,Fskill set, senior decision making,
OL,18,Fthings that will make that extra bit
OL,19,Fof difference to give the patient a
OL,20,Fbetter outcome.
